# Never copy host-installed deps into images — each Dockerfile runs its own
# `pnpm install` in-image. Copying host node_modules shadows that install with
# stale/dangling pnpm symlinks (e.g. tsx@4.22.3 vs the freshly-resolved 4.22.4),
# which breaks `tsx`-based runtime CMDs (api, web).
**/node_modules
node_modules

# Build artifacts / local cruft — regenerated in-image where needed.
**/.next
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
.git
.claude
.codex
.cursor
.vscode
